{"word":"H892 - בָּבָה - bâbâh - baw-baw' - Apple","slug":"H892","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּבָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bâbâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>baw-baw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Apple"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05D1;&#x05D4; - ba&#x0302;ba&#x0302;h</b> - <i>baw-baw'</i><p/>Feminine active participle of an unused root meaning to <i>hollow</i> out; something <i>hollowed</i> (as a <i>gate</i>), that is, the <i>pupil</i> of the eye: - apple [of the eye]."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H887\">H887</a>, <a href=\"#/H889\">H889</a>, <a href=\"#/H890\">H890</a>, <a href=\"#/H891\">H891</a>, <a href=\"#/H893\">H893</a>, <a href=\"#/H894\">H894</a>"}]}